{"lemma":"صُولِ","slug":"صُولِ","root":"ص.#.ل","root_slug":"ص-_-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-_-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n25243"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%8F%D9%88%D9%84%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to extract by means of water, to wash out"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of صَالَ (ṣāla)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n25243","headword_ar":"صوّل","root":"Swl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", and its inf. n.: see 1, last sentence but one. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taSowiylN","text_ar":"تَصْوِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extracting a thing by means of water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA: [in the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAlmAli","text_ar":"بالمالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlmaA='i","text_ar":"بِالمَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) like the extracting a pebble from rice [by washing]. (TA.) [And app. The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soaking"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to extract the juice"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bitterness"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miSowalN","text_ar":"مِصْوَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". See also an ex. in De Sacy's Chrest. Arabe, sec. ed., vol. ii. p. 130 of the Ar. text; and see his remarks thereon in p. 335 of the transl. and notes.] ―         -b3-  [Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mixing, and stirring about, and beating,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing.] One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AljaraAdu yuSaw~alu fiY mi$owaAhu","text_ar":"الجَرَادُ يُصَوَّلُ فِى مِشْوَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$wAhu","text_ar":"مَشواهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is a mistranscription,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The locusts are mixed, and stirred about, and beaten, in his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mi$owaY","text_ar":"مِشْوَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"frying-pan."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TK.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}